🛠️ Project Title: Data Exporter App

🎯 Goal:
    Build a C++17 console application that reads a dataset and exports it in different formats (like JSON, CSV, XML) using 
    different strategies, utilizing Template Method as the core.

🧩 Design Patterns Used:
    Pattern	            Purpose
    Template Method	    Define the skeleton of export steps in a base class.
    Factory Method	    Instantiate the correct exporter class based on user input.
    Strategy	        Choose the data formatting strategy dynamically.
    Singleton	        Used for configuration or logging manager.


📁 Project Structure:

    DataExporterApp/
    ├── CMakeLists.txt
    ├── main.cpp
    ├── include/
    │   ├── Exporter.hpp
    │   ├── CSVExporter.hpp
    │   ├── JSONExporter.hpp
    │   ├── XMLExporter.hpp
    │   ├── ExporterFactory.hpp
    │   ├── Logger.hpp
    │   └── FormatStrategy.hpp
    ├── src/
    │   ├── Exporter.cpp
    │   ├── CSVExporter.cpp
    │   ├── JSONExporter.cpp
    │   ├── XMLExporter.cpp
    │   ├── ExporterFactory.cpp
    │   ├── Logger.cpp
    │   └── FormatStrategy.cpp
    └── data/
        └── sample.txt
